s confederacy in our every deliberation we must consider the impact of our decisions on the next seven generations” replogle previously served as president and ceo of burts bees prior to that john spent three years at unilever where he managed the skin care division and helped to launch the real beauty campaign for dove and establish the dove selfesteem fund for young girls prior to unilever he spent eight years with diageo as president of guinness bass import company and managing director of guinness great britain he has also held several other roles in marketing sales and strategy with diageo replogle began his career as a consultant with the boston consulting group he is an active proponent of education and humanitarian causes serving on the boards of habitat for humanity and dartmouth college after receiving his ab in government from dartmouth replogle earned an mba from harvard graduating with distinction his volunteer work at dartmouth includes roles as head agent and class agent for the alumni fund along with leadership roles on the reunion giving committee he has also served as minireunion chair treasurer and vice president for the class of ’ john and his wife kristin have four daughters apply give contact dartmouth thayer express th anniversary   trustees of dartmouth collegeall rights reserved about seventh generation  seventh generation jump to navigation find a retailer faqs contact us seventh generation  years creating powerful plantbased solutions for your home  family search form search menu search productsusahouseholdbotanical disinfectants dishwashing hand soap laundryfabric softeners laundry detergent stain removers recycled paper  trash bagsnapkins paper towels tissues toilet paper trash bags surface cleaners ultra power plus free  clearbaby dishwashing laundry surface cleaners babydiapers  wipesdiapers wipes baby skin care home cleaning  laundry feminine careorganic tampons pads canadahouseholdlaundry dishwashing botanical disinfectants surface c